<!-- ============= Introduction ============================== -->
<sect1 id="geyes-introduction">
<title>介紹</title>
<!-- ==== Figure ============================================= -->
	 <figure id="geyes-fig"> 
		<title>&applet; Applet</title>
		<screenshot>
		  <mediaobject>
			 <imageobject><imagedata fileref="figures/geyes_applet.png" format="PNG"/> 
			 </imageobject>
			 <textobject>
				<phrase>顯示 Geyes Applet。</phrase>
			 </textobject>
		  </mediaobject>
		</screenshot>
	 </figure>
    <!-- ==== End of Figure ======================================= -->
<para><application>&applet;</application> Applet 可以讓您追蹤螢幕上滑鼠指標的移動。Applet 會顯示為一或多個眼睛的影像，跟著滑鼠指標在螢幕上四處移動。</para>
<para>如果要將 <application>&applet;</application> 加入面板，請在面板上按滑鼠右鍵，然後選擇<menuchoice><guimenu>加入面板</guimenu><guisubmenu>娛樂</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Geyes</guimenuitem>
</menuchoice>。</para>
</sect1>
<!-- ============= Preferences  ================================ -->
<sect1 id="geyes-settings"><title>偏好設定</title>
<para>如果要配置 <application>&applet;</application>，請在 <application>&applet;</application> Applet 上按滑鼠右鍵，然後選擇<guimenu>偏好設定</guimenu>。</para>
<variablelist>
<varlistentry>
<term><guilabel>桌面配色</guilabel> </term>
<listitem>
<para>請從這個清單中選擇 <application>&applet;</application> 的配色。
從恐怖到奇異的各種配色，為 <application>&applet;</application> 提供各種不同的外觀。</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</sect1>
